{"tid":88971,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"留下差跟壞 請表態 若不選你便任人指派","createTime":"2017-01-21T04:33:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-21T05:25:19.000Z","uid":2265,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a8724f3f03a0d2866bb2a848edcfef15ed0f8bfe","tid":88971,"uid":2265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T04:33:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0MMhVTiiZDI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0MMhVTiiZDI&d=JoJplUMG5spuYUmwSQcW9JkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=233573de\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0MMhVTiiZDI</a><br />\n壞與更壞<br />\n作詞：黃偉文   作曲：林家謙<br />\n<br />\n原來現實 與那 理想總不太同 <br />\n在谷底 哪有天虹 <br />\n「捱下去」「別放棄」 日日說金句 証明無用 <br />\n絕非 雞湯 那樣濃 <br />\n<br />\n原來落敗百次 也不可黑變紅 <br />\n做媽媽 生出「成功」 <br />\n誰又夠 運氣去 任擇 各種美滿回頭路 <br />\n常餐 得「死」與「病痛」 <br />\n<br />\n無論多麼壞 好心態 <br />\n若早知最壞 尚能更壞 <br />\n凡事都很壞 仍能 愉快 <br />\n才是崇高境&sim;界 <br />\n<br />\n離場或是勉強 結果都一個人 <br />\n二揀一 都很殘忍 <br />\n明白到 遇上你 盡力 也只配有場遺憾 <br />\n自選輕傷 更聰敏 <br />\n<br />\n無論多麼壞 好心態 <br />\n若早知最壞 尚能更壞 <br />\n凡事都很壞 仍能 愉快 <br />\n才是崇高境&sim;界 <br />\n<br />\n留下差跟壞 請表態 <br />\n若不選 你便 任人指派 <br />\n研習於失敗 維持 歡&sim;快 <br />\n才是崇高境&sim;界 <br />\n別乾等 美麗的新世界"},{"pid":"42f50c26139a8bbfe3ea1bc93a84a1ce426cf283","tid":88971,"uid":2265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T04:33:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cf4a9d48e7d4396dca787659ca751a64115492a","tid":88971,"uid":2265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T04:36:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"080c5a2873ebddb5ad81060c89c2c0b3a42d45d2","tid":88971,"uid":2265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T04:37:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29708fa2d4842c49dc6c7227564acbdd3d4d179e","tid":88971,"uid"